What are servlets ?
-------------------
	Servlets are the JAVA programming language claas which is basically use to handle the
	request-response from the servers programming module.The servlet container is the part of 
	web server which can be run in a separate process. In which we can manage data validation
	we can create the presentation logic on the client side  
	
	
What is the role of request Dispatcher Servlet?
-----------------------------------------------
	The DispatcherServlet is the front controller in Spring web applications. It's used to create 
	web applications and REST services in Spring MVC. In a traditional Spring web application, this 
	servlet is defined in the web. xml file.